Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:03.52,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Captain Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:06.94,B2,FEMALE SOUL REAPERS,0000,0000,0000,,-Captain Omaeda! \N-Captain Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:10.65,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a miracle! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:50.74,B2,OMAEDA?(talking in his sleep),0000,0000,0000,,Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.47,B2,OMAEDA?(talking in his sleep),0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Soi Fon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:04.64,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Must've been dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:08.43,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,That dream sure felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:11.00,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:19.62,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my god! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.25,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was only going to take a short nap,  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:23.16,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I slept for three hours! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.79,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm such an idiot! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:27.09,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be in big trouble if{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:28.81,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I make Captain Soi Fon mad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.37,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta get back quickly! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.44,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,That's as far as you'll get!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:02.49,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.46,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,A Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.78,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:22.30,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,In my current state, \NI'm at a disadvantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.14,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:28.85,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought there was a Hollow here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.01,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.46,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:33.63,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:34.44,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:38.65,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:39.65,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.15,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:42.03,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.95,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Please at least tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:46.89,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.19,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:52.60,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...with the Thirteen \NCourt Guard Squads...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.96,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.42,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 2 Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.92,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,You're...a...captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.38,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I blurted that out without thinking. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:10.43,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well, he's just one kid. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:20.49,B2,VILLAGER A,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, thank you so much for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.75,B2,VILLAGER A,0000,0000,0000,,saving Ryuzaburo's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.95,B2,VILLAGERC,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a drink, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.41,B2,YOUNG WOMEN,0000,0000,0000,,-Captain!\N-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.91,B2,YOUNG WOMEN,0000,0000,0000,,-Captain!\N-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.87,B2,CHILDREN,0000,0000,0000,,-Captain!\N-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.75,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, who cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.86,B2,VILLAGER C,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:40.46,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:45.34,B2,VILLAGER B,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, bring more food for the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.45,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,So? Did you really go to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.03,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,the Hollow's cave and get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.03,0:04:52.18,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:55.69,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,I win the game of courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.73,B2,BOY A/BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,-Awesome.\N-Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:01.07,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,But you had help from a captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.15,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.21,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,There's no rule that says
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.69,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,someone can't help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:08.61,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,This is a blast! A blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.31,B2,VILLAGER B,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Let's have another round over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:11.97,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.04,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.06,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.46,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, you're our hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.14,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be like you, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.55,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come to visit us again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:26.43,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I'm always willing \Nto look after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:28.51,B2,RYUZABURO ET AL,0000,0000,0000,,-Captain!\N-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:30.68,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.99,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:47.69,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.70,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be idly spending time here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.70,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,No, really, it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:56.67,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I saved a kid named Ryuzaburo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.79,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,from a Hollow, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:01.61,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Really, seriously! Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:04.96,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, there's no \Nreason why I'd be tardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:07.59,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't neglect my squad duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.76,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:12.45,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Your presence wouldn't be missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.22,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad when you put it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.98,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you're to work at
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.74,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,cleaning the Seireitei \Ngrounds for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.15,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,By yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.82,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious! What's with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.02,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Clean, by myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:27.95,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I am a lieutenant, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.20,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.28,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:35.08,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Your presence wouldn't be missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:39.04,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,But I... Yes, ma'am...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:43.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,If you could come,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.00,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,there wasn't any need for me to come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.58,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:48.37,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.72,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,Because, boys, it's not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:55.55,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like to let you in,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:57.35,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't allow anyone to go any
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.23,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,further without the permission \Nof a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.86,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,We're telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.14,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Once we see the Captain, he'll know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.15,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends of the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.33,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:11.01,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jidanbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.52,0:07:13.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.39,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,You're a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.93,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.39,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:23.33,B2,JIDANBO,0000,0000,0000,,These kids insist that I let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.87,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,We beg you! Please let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.84,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to see the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.10,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:33.39,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain saved me from a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.69,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,We showed our appreciation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.32,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,but he disappeared all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:47.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi, isn't there something we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.79,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.95,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take responsibility. \NLet these kids in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is this Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.65,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...we don't know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.90,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.93,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, was there something about
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:07.56,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,the Captain that stood out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.24,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,He was kind of husky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.92,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,And huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.58,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,And pointy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.30,B2,ICHIGO (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,Husky...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.60,B2,YORUICHI (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,Huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:23.17,B2,ICHIGO (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,And pointy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Kenpachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.39,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,But couldn't you say \NKomamura is pointy, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.53,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Around the ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.13,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,No... That guy stands out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:38.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinarily, wouldn't they \Nsay he looks like a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:41.54,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... He said he was the captain of Squad 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.54,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:50.13,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to do this sort of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:52.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:55.34,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Omaeda... Just the man I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.01,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask him where Soi Fon is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:58.89,B2,ICHIGO / YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,-Huh?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:08:59.52,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,-Captain!\N-Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.26,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.27,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,You guys?! What're you all doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:07.17,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.99,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave so suddenly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.59,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm...you know...it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.95,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no!  What should I do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.03,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lied about being a captain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.10,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and ate and drink so much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.65,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't turn back now. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.54,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Omaeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.62,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, your name is Sir Omaeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:32.40,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.77,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.96,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,addressing the Captain with no respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:35.97,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:37.92,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You say "Captain," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.01,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of Squad 2 is Soi-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.64,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.86,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,This, and then that, and whatchamacallit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.59,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.78,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:56.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but that's just lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:56.93,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.65,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Yoruichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:01.49,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I owe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.88,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, this sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.50,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe this person. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.17,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.49,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where the Captain lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:15.63,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! He's the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:18.98,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you boys have seen enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.59,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry on home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.76,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.85,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,We want to see a little more of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.56,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,the Captain doing your job!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.92,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.70,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.24,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,By Captain Omaeda's authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.07,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,you boys can do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.31,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,No...that's not a good...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:41.15,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.49,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's having fun with this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:55.13,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Madarame and Ayasegawa... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:58.59,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a troublesome pair to run into. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:00.68,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. \NYo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.82,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.75,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:10.05,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,You people owe Captain Omaeda
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.16,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,a more proper greeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.27,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Greeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.55,B2,OMAEDA (SOFTLY),0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:17.71,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Like this! Standing at attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.25,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning, sir!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.20,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,Now you try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.44,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny thing for you kids to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:27.70,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you off \Njust because you're kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.45,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.77,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:36.17,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:39.23,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll make \Nit up to you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:40.78,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.46,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ikkaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.81,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Captain Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.42,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.38,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:52.65,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,It's an easy side job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:55.61,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... This is an expense I don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.34,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you thirsty, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.94,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you two! Bring him tea right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.41,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Tea, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.67,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.26,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, Omaeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.40,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.32,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting out of here while I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:18.30,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.21,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Your tea is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.10,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.47,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.47,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought you your tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.68,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you here, Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.43,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Yumichika told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.35,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Right, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.95,0:12:35.35,B2,FEMALE SOUL REAPERS,0000,0000,0000,,-Captain Omaeda!\N-Captain Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.02,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,You people, take the Captain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.68,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,somewhere where he can relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.95,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.32,B2,SOUL REAPERS,0000,0000,0000,,-Yes!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:47.32,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:56.52,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,They took my wallet, my watch, \Nmy ring...everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.81,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,This is costing me big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:12:59.46,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.49,B2,SOIFON (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.66,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything left to give you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.44,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Captain...Soi Fon! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.30,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to be
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.40,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,on cleaning duties by \Nyourself for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.44,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.22,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no... This is bad...seriously bad! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.35,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.97,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.12,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:37.13,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.96,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way to speak to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:43.30,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, don't! Not this person! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.04,B2,BOY A/BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,-Just who do you think this\N-Just who do you think this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.76,B2,BOY A/BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,-person before you is?!\N-person before you is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.97,B2,RYUZABURO ET AL,0000,0000,0000,,-He is Sir Omaeda,\N-He is Sir Omaeda,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.47,B2,RYUZABURO ET AL,0000,0000,0000,,-captain of Squad 2!\N-captain of Squad 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:56.23,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those canned lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.90,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.03,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Marechiyo, you're in serious trouble! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.85,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goodbye, my days in Seireitei... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:10.66,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello, unknown future. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.79,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm done for. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:20.88,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Captain Omaeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.26,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A miracle! This is a miracle! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.84,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've truly been saved by the gods! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.35,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it really okay to let this go on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:32.14,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.66,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said that from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.54,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Sir Omaeda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.73,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,Give this misguided woman orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.69,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.50,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You were saying something earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.23,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,about cleaning by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.38,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh she is enjoying this so much. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.96,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Now... What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.72,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.48,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Another bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.51,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:09.93,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,Another bowl for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.90,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Captain is out of sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:12.60,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.31,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,What next, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.79,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:25.64,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spot. Harder, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.92,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.97,0:15:35.90,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we came!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.73,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.12,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,We're so lucky to have \Nmet such a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.32,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:41.81,B2,IKKAKU (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.46,B2,IKKAKU (VOICE),0000,0000,0000,,That bastard Omaeda was so insulting to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.21,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,That coward could never be a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.97,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway you look at it,\Nhe hasn't got what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:51.92,B2,YUMICHIKA,0000,0000,0000,,His face, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.43,B2,IKKAKU,0000,0000,0000,,I swear. I'm going to kill him! \NWhat did he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.68,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,It means he was lying \Nabout everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:56.95,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaburo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.43,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,Captain nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:01.00,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,We acted like fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.27,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.21,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.32,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you come,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.78,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I will look after you as the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.11,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.37,B2,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:23.43,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Ryuzaburo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.91,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, shall I give you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.49,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,some training in swordsmanship?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.80,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become strong like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:32.61,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.71,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.03,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.84,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.84,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:48.91,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:51.01,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.26,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:02.35,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Now give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.55,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,This is the piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.80,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,With this, my powers will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.98,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to devour you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:31.84,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.66,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,You keep adding one hassle after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:39.95,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here and be still!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.62,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:48.63,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:50.49,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can catch
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:52.30,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,me with that slowness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.19,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.28,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.99,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,My movements may not be that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:09.47,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,But if I use the power of my tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:13.44,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,I can completely suppress \Nthe speed of my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.22,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.28,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bastard... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.91,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He suppressed my speed. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:21.46,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.33,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is really bad! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.71,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to get help immediately. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:33.97,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are they doing here? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:37.13,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... I'm a... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.79,0:18:41.30,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a captain in front of those kids! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.72,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And a captain... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.68,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A captain shouldn't... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.16,B2,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,He's no good, just like they said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:04.48,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,He's different, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.99,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What's different?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:08.69,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:11.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the guy's not a captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.62,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't change the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,fact that he saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:20.22,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Was it the title of captain
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:21.86,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,that you were appreciative of?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:24.67,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Or were you appreciative of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,the guy who saved you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This time, keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.90,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.82,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd be running away by now if {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.89,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they weren't looking at me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.91,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I can't run away, not with {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.74,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the speed I have in these legs. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.29,B2,OMAEDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? If they weren't looking at me... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.91,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Gave up so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:53.13,B2,HOLLOW,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's time I devoured you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:03.61,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How does Gegetsuburi taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:09.77,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Bakudo Number 21: Sekienton!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.02,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.56,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Can't see me very well, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:21.07,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see you, either...but \Nthat doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:22.49,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Smash'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.45,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:44.28,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Omaeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.96,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Demoted from "Captain" \Nto "Mister," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.53,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say? You lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.23,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.39,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,But it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.77,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,My friends said they want to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.02,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,become strong Soul Reapers like you, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.36,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:05.48,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.48,0:21:07.49,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become a stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:08.87,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,lieutenant than you, Mr. Omaeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.42,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.94,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.71,0:21:14.56,B2,RYUZABURO,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:24.01,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,All's well that ends well, eh, Omaeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.92,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:29.90,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go back and have some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:30.93,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.73,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.39,0:21:39.14,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!\NI suppose he brought this on himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.72,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I just got my public\NI suppose he brought this on himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,image to look good!\NYou're one to talk, Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:46.37,B2,OMAEDA (disbelieving),0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:22.04,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:23.82,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.63,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi, open the Senkaimon will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:26.51,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.51,0:23:27.59,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:28.62,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more stories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.62,0:23:30.09,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,like this coming up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:31.14,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,We're having you get caught up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:33.11,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,in another mess for the next episode as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:34.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Please, enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.19,0:23:36.82,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:37.69,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:38.43,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:39.87,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:41.56,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.19,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Lies have their uses, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:45.44,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.65,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:47.85,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:48.87,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,But it's also said that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.87,0:23:50.99,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,what goes around comes around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:51.63,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:52.41,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:54.48,B2,OMAEDA,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch ouch ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:58.06,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,But "tread on a worm and \Nit will turn on you."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.08,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:01.00,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,You had it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:01.79,B2,SOI FON,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:04.46,B2,YORUICHI,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:06.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,